Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Congress vote on MX missile
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wx28
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Dec 1982
Extra funding for MX missile gets Congress go-ahead despite fears over bases. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less